</span><span>        The original </span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">code</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span>chat.html</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">code</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span> and </span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">code</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span>conversation.json</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">code</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span> files were too large (approximately 200 MB each) to upload directly to GitHub, exceeding the free Git LFS storage limit and causing upload issues. To resolve this, we split both files into smaller chunks of approximately 5 MB each using a Bash script. These chunks are stored in the </span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">code</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span>chunks/</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">code</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span> directory with prefixes </span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">code</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span>chat_part_</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">code</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span> and </span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">code</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span>conversation_part_</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">code</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span> (e.g., </span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">code</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span>chunks/chat_part_aa</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">code</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span>, </span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">code</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span>chunks/conversation_part_ab</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">code</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span>, etc.).
