</span><span>        </span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">li</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span>Smaller chunks are easier to manage, especially on systems with limited resources.</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/</span><span class="hljs-tag" style="color: rgb(224, 108, 117);">li</span><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span><span>
